erica in  our vision is to become a fully integrated global automotive supplier said vinnie johnson  amit is a resultsoriented leader with global operational and financial experience  he will provide additional strategic direction and oversight at a group level to help us reach new higher levels of performance in the years ahead singhi holds masters degrees in electrical engineering and business administration from the university of michigan in ann arbor and a bachelors degree in electrical engineering from the indian institute of technology in mumbai india trending amazon and general electric are fridays smoking hot tickers amzn tsla sbux ge aapl apple investing billions in oled display here is why jim cramer doesnt want to buy more starbucks shares for action alerts plus amazon and starbucks team up to take down nasdaq exxon mobil stock tanks on earnings miss advertising partners  thestreet inc all rights reservedaction alerts plus is a registered trademark of thestreet inc compare brokers amit singhi  flir systems inc  email cfosvp finance flircom login  day free trial amit singhi flir systems inc cfosvp finance updated on  jun   export  sw parkway avenue wilsonville or  email format for flircom direct phone not available type public employees    revenue   billion industry materialsmanufacturing sic code   search and navigation equipment biography flir systems incs cfosvp finance is amit singhi they are based in wilsonville or and you can find their lead profile filed under the materialsmanufacturing industry amit singhis profile contains twitter phone numbers linkedin wiki and biography information and you can also find other flir systems inc contact information and email addresses on lead with the flircom domain format some possible email formats for amit singhi are asinghiflircom amitsinghiflircom amitflircom and amitsinghiflircom if you sign up for our free trial you will see our emailflircom addresses similar people amit s  other need to know amit ss email p